Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.10,0:01:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姓佐伯的男人\N不是普通的企業家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.40,0:01:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.43,0:01:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他另有目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.00,0:01:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.68,0:02:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然被知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.01,0:02:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就封住你的口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.06,0:02:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,縛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.00,0:02:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你水平差多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.34,0:02:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.20,0:03:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第九十二話\N東京府戒嚴\N狂暴進擊的兇器 龍脈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.52,0:03:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.29,0:03:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靈水在大陸徹底學會\N大陸風水術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.30,0:03:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是大和風水嚴禁的禁術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.17,0:03:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入邪之法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.74,0:03:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傷口會自然吸收邪氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.34,0:03:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由內使身體腐敗的邪門之術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.48,0:03:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太…太慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.25,0:03:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風 有辦法醫治嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.75,0:03:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有 去武藏野之泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.69,0:03:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武藏野…難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.82,0:04:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 佐伯挖洞想控制龍脈的根源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.76,0:04:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武藏野之泉從太古時代\N就是充滿強力的龍泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.03,0:04:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用那泉水的水清洗傷口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.44,0:04:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該就可以救回阿薰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.27,0:04:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼快點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.74,0:04:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風 麻煩你帶路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.25,0:04:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何\N我一定要得到那個泉水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.62,0:04:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.25,0:04:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下\N路上會發生什麼危險不曉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.92,0:04:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是保護小姐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.82,0:04:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的對 禰彥\N這就是你的工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.90,0:04:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們差不多該走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.57,0:04:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.87,0:04:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村 我等你的好消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.44,0:04:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫軍官們到兵部省集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.21,0:04:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始評定府內的戒備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.58,0:04:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.35,0:05:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.92,0:05:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞上二樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.09,0:05:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,金庫是空的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.39,0:05:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二樓什麼人也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.36,0:05:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.30,0:05:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點不用你說也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.47,0:05:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何一定要找出佐伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.04,0:05:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動員警視廳所有的警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.64,0:05:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.78,0:05:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對他們而言\N這個道場已經沒用處了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.45,0:05:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不大可能再來襲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.82,0:05:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我想拜託二位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.42,0:05:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐伯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.65,0:05:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破壞永恆之陣後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.86,0:05:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該會設下新的魔法陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.23,0:05:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然 他會進入那建築物的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.73,0:05:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我不知數目會是多少\N就麻煩你全部找出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.80,0:05:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要打死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.00,0:05:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼好認的特徵嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.37,0:05:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,69307AF0里鬼門的海獅子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.90,0:05:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及類似的建築物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.24,0:05:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.31,0:06:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.61,0:06:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從那名字看來是風之一族了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.84,0:06:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那族\N應該在很久以前就消失呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.25,0:06:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們勉勉強強傳承下來\N那傢伙大概是明後的存活者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.22,0:06:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼 我一定殺死他\N你不必擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.09,0:06:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 那麼我來報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.34,0:07:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅牛、神谷、\N以及其他魔法陣都成功破壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.31,0:07:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我導入龍脈的一部份到府內\N把工部省破壞掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.32,0:07:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要確實擊破最終目標的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.12,0:07:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重是要一舉破壞迂迴到\N武藏野東北方的龍脈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.62,0:07:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以在那以前\N我們還得做更多實驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.16,0:07:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前下一個目標是司法省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.70,0:07:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及警視廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.50,0:07:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最終目標是天老院吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.37,0:07:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 但是真正目標\N是下周在這裏召開的太政會議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.91,0:07:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有參議的高官\N都會聚集在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.05,0:07:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而會議中發動龍脈\N攻擊這裏的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.42,0:07:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可以瞬間消滅\N代表這個國家的高官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.82,0:07:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且這裏是\N德川家康永恆之陣的樞紐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.96,0:07:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可說是一舉二得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.83,0:07:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破壞德川家康永恆之陣\N建立新的魔法陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是水之一族的心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.44,0:08:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再同是殺掉所有的高官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.74,0:08:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天下就是我們的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.64,0:08:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會議確實會召開嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.38,0:08:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 由於我的巨額賄賂\N太政官完全聽從我的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.62,0:08:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不知道自己將會被殺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.55,0:08:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愚蠢的明治新政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.82,0:08:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,口上說要維新
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.33,0:08:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在仍然依賴\N德川家康的永恆之陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.56,0:08:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在魔法陣的重鎮建立政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.67,0:08:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這將成為他們的致命傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.57,0:08:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我要讓他們知道\N水之一族有多可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.88,0:09:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(咒)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.62,0:10:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心點 慢慢來哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.16,0:10:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.22,0:10:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對…我的任務是把它找出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.39,0:10:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.83,0:10:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,專門讓我做重勞動工作嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.96,0:10:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊的工程 慢著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.37,0:10:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.49,0:10:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到下一個地方去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是猴子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.10,0:10:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.64,0:10:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是警視廳？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.28,0:10:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,署長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,署長 你在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.15,0:11:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.22,0:11:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,川…川路警視 警視廳被毀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.59,0:11:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 這個看就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.42,0:11:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我問你調查得怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.12,0:11:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行呀 連相關的公司人士\N都沒人知道他在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.16,0:11:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就猜到是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.10,0:11:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情不會這樣就結束的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.90,0:11:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會結束的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.28,0:11:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沉眠在地下的氣脈之泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.71,0:11:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到關東有這樣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.22,0:11:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到江戶這個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.92,0:11:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是德川家康好運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.02,0:11:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個地方是地脈的寶庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.42,0:11:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以德川的天下\N才能維持三百年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.87,0:11:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對阿薰施下咒術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.21,0:12:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是要我們\N引誘到武藏野的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.41,0:12:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我一定會活著回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.48,0:12:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.02,0:12:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概在黑船來日本的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.25,0:12:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟一個女人共同生活過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.09,0:12:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那段間很短…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.79,0:12:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有天早上我醒來女人不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.43,0:12:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留下一封信說：
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.56,0:12:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的妻子不是我  是大和風水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.90,0:12:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托她的福\N風之一族在我這一代就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.44,0:12:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村 風水與劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.11,0:12:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本來以為我們是同類人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.78,0:12:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來我看錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.58,0:12:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.18,0:12:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要珍惜她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.49,0:12:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,汲汲忙於鑽研自己的道路\N下場就是像我這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.23,0:12:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求道很重要 但不該被束縛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人活著要有價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我們守護住現在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了要活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.07,0:13:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在工部省之後\N接著是司法省與警視廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.58,0:13:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而逃離東京的人也在增加中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.48,0:13:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說已加強戒備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.75,0:13:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是沒辦法阻止那崩潰現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.12,0:13:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不得已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.32,0:13:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,近衛出動所有第一近衛大隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要出動大隊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.50,0:13:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 現在起近衛大隊\N全數投入武藏野
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.43,0:13:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破壞佐伯的鐵路工程現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.44,0:13:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且 由我親自指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.27,0:13:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動作快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.93,0:14:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要等到夜裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.56,0:14:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照月岡所說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.33,0:14:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工程不分日夜在進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.60,0:14:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等到深夜…也不會有多少改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.87,0:14:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.34,0:14:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且時間寶貴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.11,0:14:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.81,0:14:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.68,0:14:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼  怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.19,0:14:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,借過！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.32,0:14:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,烈！爆！破！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.93,0:14:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是警視廳的川路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.70,0:14:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山縣大人在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.54,0:14:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人現在不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.14,0:14:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這是幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.61,0:14:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警視廳無法使用\N我們要暫時借用這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.98,0:14:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太突然了 我沒有那權限啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.65,0:14:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們很急 借過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.25,0:15:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水泉位置呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.42,0:15:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之在後面 一直跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.96,0:15:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣！旋風波！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.27,0:15:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.84,0:15:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.88,0:15:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個隧道被設下\N封印風水術的魔法陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.08,0:15:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是感應到\N我風水術自動反擊的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.09,0:15:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邪鏡之陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.69,0:15:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說你的風水術就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.99,0:15:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們先趕路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.37,0:15:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.44,0:15:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了 小心點 左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.18,0:15:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.18,0:16:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.42,0:16:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒到那座泉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.33,0:16:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.93,0:16:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.48,0:16:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏…這個隧道已經沒路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.92,0:16:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是防衛泉水\N免受外敵侵犯的五芒星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.29,0:16:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍脈的力量增幅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.03,0:16:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們以水泉為中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.83,0:16:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刻意增幅\N對流在這附近的龍脈的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼一來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.97,0:17:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們想利用龍脈\N來破解永恆之陣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.04,0:17:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我想不透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.68,0:17:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏到府內有相當遠的距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.82,0:17:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管他們怎樣增強力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.92,0:17:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等龍脈到達府內的時候\N力量已經衰減了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.63,0:17:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.33,0:17:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那還用說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.03,0:17:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破壞五芒星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.87,0:17:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你說過\N這裏使用風水術會有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.57,0:17:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了得到泉水 沒別的辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.64,0:17:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村 你退後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.58,0:17:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.05,0:17:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,式神們就讓你處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.02,0:17:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.42,0:18:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(咒)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.40,0:18:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,烈！爆！破！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.82,0:18:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.39,0:18:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.03,0:18:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.11,0:18:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.78,0:18:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,順著牆壁上刻劃的螺旋凹紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.71,0:18:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣流去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.78,0:18:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣流順著直線流出\N會成為自然界之福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.75,0:18:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 順著螺旋方向流出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.65,0:18:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那速度會越來越快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.19,0:19:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣脈的純度\N會超過極限而提高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.06,0:19:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超過極限的高純度的氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.50,0:19:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經是邪惡的兇器了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.10,0:19:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道…他們是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.64,0:19:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故意在武藏野刻劃螺旋溝\N導引龍脈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.48,0:19:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們還在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.31,0:19:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我試著用平息之陣看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.15,0:19:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.76,0:19:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.76,0:19:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我要用我\N體內殘存的所有的氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.66,0:19:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平息這個龍脈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.13,0:19:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.10,0:19:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平息之陣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.33,0:19:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(咒)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.94,0:19:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍脈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下這個氣 平息吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以步上邪惡之道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.91,0:19:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍脈呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.34,0:20:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把心平靜下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.04,0:20:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以誤信\N水之一族的片面之言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.61,0:20:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以把力量拿來為惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.95,0:20:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 你要去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.15,0:20:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底想去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.79,0:20:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風 這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.03,0:20:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.20,0:20:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個隧道撐不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.57,0:20:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.14,0:20:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,汲水呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.10,0:20:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.82,0:21:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.02,0:21:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.22,0:21:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的給阿薰用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.96,0:21:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.56,0:21:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現緋村與陣風兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.94,0:21:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山縣大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.51,0:21:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來我們是白來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.84,0:21:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太佩服你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.05,0:21:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 事情並沒有解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.18,0:21:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們好像把隧道擊碎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.09,0:21:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那只是單純的龍脈的噴出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.12,0:21:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍脈已經步上往東北方的路線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.86,0:21:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下子武藏野就沒用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.50,0:21:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幽水\N我要跟龍脈一起去東北方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.54,0:21:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,府內的事就交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.47,0:22:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.07,0:22:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍脈已經啟動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.34,0:22:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下子任何人都不能阻止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.51,0:22:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道沒有辦法阻止嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.05,0:22:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要讓以螺旋狀飛出的龍脈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.15,0:22:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再度回到府內\N而且正確碰上永恆之陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.56,0:22:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,需在某個地方\N設下固定方向的魔法陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.36,0:22:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以要先發制人\N破壞那個魔法陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.53,0:22:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那地方是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.37,0:22:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在武藏野的東北方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.24,0:22:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日光！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.61,0:22:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日光…

